\b\fs26 Advanced Technical Solutions\b0\fs24\par
\par

\b The 1+1=3 Problem: Emergence Value Recognition\b0\par
Problem: When ideas combine to create more value than their sum\par
Solution: Emergence Premium Distribution\par
\bullet 40% to original idea creators\par
\bullet 50% to person who saw the combination\par
\bullet 10% to fund future emergence research\par
\par

\b Recursive Attribution Management\b0\par
Problem: Who gets credit for improving the attribution system itself?\par
Solution: Constitutional Framework with Finite Recursion\par
\bullet 70% to improvement creator\par
\bullet 20% to original system creators\par
\bullet 10% to recursive improvement fund\par
\bullet Constitutional limits prevent infinite regress\par
\par

\b Adversarial Defense Framework\b0\par
The Big Four Threat Categories:\par
\par
1. \b Attribution Gaming\b0 - Fake conversations, synthetic contributions\par
   Defense: Semantic fingerprinting, behavioral analysis, reputation staking\par
\par
2. \b Economic Manipulation\b0 - Market manipulation, payment gaming\par
   Defense: Temporal decay algorithms, circuit breakers, diversification requirements\par
\par
3. \b Governance Capture\b0 - Stake accumulation, voting manipulation\par
   Defense: Constitutional constraints, minority protections, emergency protocols\par
\par
4. \b Epistemic Poisoning\b0 - False information injection, reality distortion\par
   Defense: Truth consensus mechanisms, source verification, contradiction detection\par
\par

\b Constitutional Governance Framework\b0\par
Immutable Principles (Cannot be changed):\par
1. Attribution Rights are Inalienable - Every human contribution must be attributed\par
2. Transparency is Mandatory - All AI reasoning must be cryptographically proven\par
3. Democratic Participation is Protected - Economic stake provides voting power\par
4. Economic Justice is Enforced - 15% minimum to commons, 20% max concentration\par
\par

\b Temporal Justice & Cultural Preservation\b0\par
\bullet Bonuses for endangered knowledge preservation\par
\bullet Anti-colonial paraphrasing detection\par
\bullet Cultural preservation multipliers\par
\bullet Oral tradition documentation incentives\par
\bullet Indigenous knowledge protection mechanisms\par
\par

